          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Framer gets you <span class="text-[#8B5CF6]">40% higher conversion</span> on average. Wix gets you <span class="text-orange-400">500 apps you'll never use</span>.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
